languages.text: "Заверяю, господин Ульфар, что и помыслить о подобном не могла. Откуда такие подозрения, вы что-то потеряли? Поищите получше в своей келье, уверена, найдете!"
"I assure you, my lord Ulfar, I would never dream of doing such a thing. Why are you acting so suspicious — have you lost something? Take a closer look in your cell, I'm sure you'll find it!"

languages.text: “我向你保证，乌尔法大人，我绝不会做这种事情。你为什么如此疑神疑鬼，莫非你真的丢了什么东西吗？不如多在房间里翻翻吧，想必一定能找到！”
languages.original_text: "I assure you, my lord Ulfar, I would never dream of doing such a thing. Why are you acting so suspicious — have you lost something? Take a closer look in your cell, I'm sure you'll find it!"

languages.text: « Je peux vous assurer, seigneur Ulfar, que jamais je n'oserais faire une chose pareille ! Que me vaut tant de suspicion ? Auriez-vous perdu quelque chose ? Vous devriez fouiller votre cellule, vous finirez bien par le retrouver ! »
languages.original_text: "I assure you, my lord Ulfar, I would never dream of doing such a thing. Why are you acting so suspicious — have you lost something? Take a closer look in your cell, I'm sure you'll find it!"

languages.text: "Ich versichere Euch, mein Lord Ulfar, ich würde nicht im Traum daran denken. Warum das Misstrauen? Habt Ihr etwas verloren? Seht in Eurer Zelle noch einmal genauer nach, Ihr findet es bestimmt!"
languages.original_text: "I assure you, my lord Ulfar, I would never dream of doing such a thing. Why are you acting so suspicious — have you lost something? Take a closer look in your cell, I'm sure you'll find it!"

languages.text: 「ウルファー様、アタシはそのようなことをしようとは夢にも思っていない。なぜそんなに疑う？何か失くしたのか？もう少し自分の部屋をよくみたら、きっと見つかるよ！」

languages.text: «Le aseguro, lord Ulfar, que nunca soñaría con hacer algo así. ¿A qué viene esa mirada suspicaz? ¿Ha perdido algo? Mire bien en su celda, ¡seguro que lo encuentra!».
